  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972520/extras/673da3586bb8e7a55302db2b4a4b9c26.poster.avif?t=1571497455\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972520/extras/673da3586bb8e7a55302db2b4a4b9c26.webm?t=1571497455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972520/extras/673da3586bb8e7a55302db2b4a4b9c26.mp4?t=1571497455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>STORY</u></strong><br>Join Melon & his buddy Dug in this Misadventure that takes him through 6 amazing chapters, Snow, Caves, Forest, Swamp, Mountains and Corrupted lands to battle through corrupted creatures and to make your way back to the village and save the world from this evil!<br><br><u><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></u><br>An old school side scrolling beat em up adventure game filled with plenty of secrets, power ups, collectibles, puzzles platforming and of course a lot of Fighting!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 Chapters<br></li><li>Over 30 hats<br></li><li>6 Secret collectibles<br></li><li>5 bonus levels <br></li><li>Challenging bosses and mini bosses<br></li><li>Loads of upgrades</li></ul><br><u><strong>CONTROLS</strong></u><br>Move: \"ARROW KEYS\"<br>Light Attack: \"A\"<br>Hard Attack: \"S\"<br>Extra/Use:    \"D\"<br>Jump: \"SPACEBAR\"",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972520/extras/673da3586bb8e7a55302db2b4a4b9c26.poster.avif?t=1571497455\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972520/extras/673da3586bb8e7a55302db2b4a4b9c26.webm?t=1571497455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972520/extras/673da3586bb8e7a55302db2b4a4b9c26.mp4?t=1571497455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>STORY</u></strong><br>Join Melon & his buddy Dug in this Misadventure that takes him through 6 amazing chapters, Snow, Caves, Forest, Swamp, Mountains and Corrupted lands to battle through corrupted creatures and to make your way back to the village and save the world from this evil!<br><br><u><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></u><br>An old school side scrolling beat em up adventure game filled with plenty of secrets, power ups, collectibles, puzzles platforming and of course a lot of Fighting!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 Chapters<br></li><li>Over 30 hats<br></li><li>6 Secret collectibles<br></li><li>5 bonus levels <br></li><li>Challenging bosses and mini bosses<br></li><li>Loads of upgrades</li></ul><br><u><strong>CONTROLS</strong></u><br>Move: \"ARROW KEYS\"<br>Light Attack: \"A\"<br>Hard Attack: \"S\"<br>Extra/Use:    \"D\"<br>Jump: \"SPACEBAR\"",
